longBusinessSummary: The Keg Royalties Income Fund operates as an unincorporated open-ended limited purpose trust. It invests in The Keg Rights Limited Partnership, which owns the trademarks, trade names, operating procedures and systems, and other intellectual property used in connection with the operation of Keg steakhouse restaurants and bars in Canada and the United Sates. The company was incorporated in 2002 and is headquartered in Richmond, Canada.
